<div>

<br />
<br />

<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">
For the seventh year running Beantown Web has conducted a 
quasi-scientific meta-search to identify the best business books published during the 
calendar year.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">The books identified in this analysis are most likely to add value to your career.
</span>

</div>

<div>
<br />
<span style="font-family: arial;"><span style="font-size: large;">This year's search began by identifying 12 "Best of" lists. This resource list is available upon request. Presented here are the results.
<br />
</span>

<br />

</span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;">A total of 104 books were mentioned on at least one "Best of" list. Of these recommendations, 78 books were mentioned only once. An additional 13 books were mentioned on two lists and these books comprise the <b>Honorable Mention</b> list.
<br />
